legacy.full_text: China shares development dividends with Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation #APEC economies. China's foreign trade with APEC economies amounted to US$3.74 trillion in 2022, accounting for 59.7% of its total. Eight of China's top 10 trading partners are APEC economies.

The 30th APEC Economic Leaders' Meeting is taking place in the U.S. city of San Francisco from Nov 15 to 17, with the theme of “Creating a Resilient and Sustainable Future for All.”It’s important for major economies to engage in talks amid an uncertain economic & political state. https://t.co/ij8YoQUa0A
